                    <h3>About the exhibition</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8            col-xs-12">
                   <p>The exhibition „INTERNET FAME“ is part of the official Embassy Program of The Wrong New Digital Art Biennale. The exhibition explores the shifting relationship between Art, Internet and Fame in the age of total digitalisation.</p>                </div>

